---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import club from "../data/club.json";
---
<Base pageTitle="Aktuelles">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <img class="page-hero__pattern" src="assets/img/hero-pattern.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="page-hero__dragon" src="assets/img/drache-light.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="wrap page-hero__inner">
      <p class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Start</a> · Aktuelles</p>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--invert">News &amp; Berichte</span>
      <h1>Aktuelles aus dem Verein</h1>
      <p>Turniererfolge, Prüfungen, Feiern – hier erfährst du, was bei {club.brand_name} los ist.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="news-grid" data-news>
        <div class="skeleton"></div><div class="skeleton"></div><div class="skeleton"></div>
        <div class="skeleton"></div><div class="skeleton"></div><div class="skeleton"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="notice notice--mock" style="margin-top:34px">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 5h16v14H4zM4 9h16M9 13h7M9 16h4"/></svg>
        <p><b>Hinweis:</b> Die Beiträge werden in dieser Demo aus einer simulierten API (<code>/api/news</code>) geladen. Inhalte lassen sich in <code>assets/data/news.json</code> pflegen.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section--tight">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-band reveal">
        <span class="cta-band__glow" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h2>Auch dabei sein?</h2>
        <p>Werde Teil unserer Erfolgsgeschichte – starte mit einem kostenlosen Probetraining.</p>
        <div class="hero__cta"><a href="anmeldung.html" class="btn btn--gold btn--lg">Jetzt mitmachen</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Fragment slot="scripts">
    <script is:inline src="assets/js/news.js"></script>
    <script is:inline src="assets/js/sponsors.js"></script>
  </Fragment>
</Base>
